<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<manifest xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android" android:versionCode="5" android:versionName="1.4.20180111" package="lt.andro.broadcastlogger">
	<uses-sdk android:minSdkVersion="14" android:targetSdkVersion="26" />
	<uses-permission android:name="android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETED" />
	<application android:theme="resourceId:0x7f0e0005" android:label="Broadcasts Monitor" android:icon="res/mipmap-anydpi-v26/ic_launcher.xml" android:debuggable="true" android:allowBackup="true">
		<activity android:label="Broadcasts Monitor" android:name="lt.andro.broadcastlogger.MainActivity">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN" />
				<category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER" />
			</intent-filter>
		</activity>
		<service android:label="Latest broadcast's action is:" android:name="lt.andro.broadcastlogger.BroadcastMonitoringService" />
		<provider android:name="lt.andro.broadcastlogger.contentprovider.BroadcastContentProvider" android:exported="false" android:authorities="lt.andro.broadcastlogger" />
		<receiver android:name="lt.andro.broadcastlogger.AnyBroadcastReceiver" android:process=":receiver">
			<intent-filter>
				<action android:name="android.intent.action.BOOT_COMPLETED" />
			</intent-filter>
		</receiver>
		<meta-data android:name="android.support.VERSION" android:value="26.1.0" />
		<meta-data android:name="android.arch.lifecycle.VERSION" android:value="27.0.0-SNAPSHOT" />
	</application>
</manifest>
